{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b3b056c286","title":"转发邓小平关于整风、春耕情况向中央的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"614897d0bd","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":13,"articleId":"b3b056c286"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"339df4e14c","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓小平，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记。"},{"id":"dbe8f17bd4","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指邓小平1950年5月11日给毛泽东并中央的电报。电报中说：西南局“确定整风的主要方法是联系实际，从检查工作入手，充分发展批评和自我批评，达到使干部提高一步的目的。整风对象着重于军队各级干部和地方三方左右的骨十，其中又以县以上十部为主。在步骤上，地方拟先由省、区党委集中县委书记以上干部整风，弄通他们是一切问题的关键；然后经过他们去领导三万人的整风。时间以半个月到二十天为度”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b341acc399","type":"title","text":"转发邓小平以关于整风、春耕情况向中央的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286"},{"id":"339df4e14c","type":"paragraph","text":"华东局，中南局，西北局，华北局，东北局，华南分局，上海市委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286"},{"id":"dbe8f17bd4","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将邓小平同志五月十一日来电转发给你们参考。其中所说整风步骤，我们认为是正确的，请你们亦照此项步骤部署进行，即先整县委书记以上，再整广大干部。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286"},{"id":"a8de013c40","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286"},{"id":"cab35cc072","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286"}],"page":{"id":"382fd58e06","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b3b056c286","start":387,"end":387}}}},"__N_SSG":true}